episodes.title: The Bad Batch
episodes.plot: Rex, Cody, and Clone Force 99 (an unorthodox, elite squad also known as the Bad Batch), look to recover the Republic's strategy algorithm from Admiral Trench, but a haunting truth awaits.

episodes.title: A Distant Echo
episodes.plot: Believing that MIA soldier Echo may still be alive, Rex's mission becomes doubly important. Alongside Bad Batch and Anakin, the clone captain launches a dangerous covert rescue.

episodes.title: On the Wings of Keeradaks
episodes.plot: With Echo recovered, Rex, Bad Batch and Anakin look to fight their way out of a Separatist base.

episodes.title: Unfinished Business
episodes.plot: The Republic plans a daring final strike against Admiral Trench, once again bringing together Rex, Echo, Anakin, and the elite Bad Batch squad.

episodes.title: Gone with a Trace
episodes.plot: After leaving the Jedi Order, Ahsoka finds herself in the underworld of Coruscant where she meets aspiring pilot, Trace Martez. Enlisted by Trace's sister, Rafa, to help build dangerous droids, Ahsoka opts to keep her Jedi past a secret.

episodes.title: Deal No Deal
episodes.plot: Ahsoka, Trace and Rafa are hired to deliver some spice, but things soon get complicated.

episodes.title: Dangerous Debt
episodes.plot: Taken prisoner by the Pykes, Ahsoka and the Martez sisters attempt to escape.

episodes.title: Together Again
episodes.plot: Ahsoka bargains for the sisters' freedom and makes a startling discovery.

episodes.title: Old Friends Not Forgotten
episodes.plot: Ahsoka contacts Anakin and Obi-Wan, who must decide whether to help her pursue Maul on Mandalore or defend Coruscant.

episodes.title: The Phantom Apprentice
episodes.plot: Ahsoka leads Republic clones to confront Maul's forces on Mandalore. Maul senses the impending chaos and makes a calculated play to ensure his own survival.

episodes.title: Shattered
episodes.plot: After capturing Maul on Mandalore, Ahsoka's journey to the Jedi Council is disrupted when Order 66 is declared, turning her world upside down.

episodes.title: Victory and Death
episodes.plot: Ahsoka and Rex must use their wit and skills to survive the turbulent end of the Clone Wars.
